abstract: Michigan officials confirm that Canada geese in state have tested positive for highly pathogenic H5N2 flu strain.
lead_paragraph: Michigan officials on Monday said that Canada geese in the state had tested positive for a lethal strain of bird flu, bringing the worst outbreak of the disease in United States history.

headline.main: Canada Geese in Michigan Discovered to Have Bird Flu
headline.print_headline: Canada Geese in Michigan Discovered to Have Bird Flu
